---
import "../styles/engagement.css"
---

<section class="engagement">
  <div class="shell">
    <header class="engagement__header">
      <!-- <p class="engagement__eyebrow">How we can work together</p> -->
      <h2 class="engagement__title">Two ways to work together</h2>
      <!-- <p class="engagement__intro">
        Choose <strong>per-project</strong> for specific decks, or an <strong
          >ongoing retainer</strong
        > for guaranteed support and regular needs
      </p> -->
    </header>
    <div class="engagement__grid">
      <article class="engagement-card">
        <h3 class="engagement-card__title">Project Basis</h3>
        <ul class="engagement-card__list">
          <li>No monthly commitment. Engage on demand.</li>
          <li>Turnaround: Subject to capacity (Typically 1–2 weeks).</li>
          <!-- <li>
            <strong>Minimum engagement:</strong> 5 hours per project. 5 hours is
            typically enough for a light polish of a 10-slide deck or full design
            of 2-3 complex slides.
          </li> -->
          <li>To reserve time and start: 5 hours prepaid.</li>
          <li>
            Rush (less than 3 business days): Available with 50% fee (preserves
            retainer priority).
          </li>
          <li>
            Send your project files and details to start. All files are treated
            as confidential.
          </li>
          <li>Expect a reply in 1-2 business days.</li>
          <li>Retainer overages are billed at this rate.</li>
          <li>
            <strong>Best for:</strong> First-time clients or occasional presentation
            design needs.
          </li>
        </ul>
        <!-- <p class="engagement-card__note">
          <strong>Best for:</strong> First-time clients or occasional presentation
          design needs.
        </p> -->
        <p class="engagement-card__note engagement-card__note--muted">
          If you upgrade to a retainer within 30 days of a project, I’ll credit
          part of the cost to your first month. (One time use)
        </p>
      </article>
      <article class="engagement-card engagement-card--highlight">
        <h3 class="engagement-card__title">Monthly Retainer</h3>
        <ul class="engagement-card__list">
          <li>High priority. Reserved capacity.</li>
          <li>One invoice, billed monthly in advance.</li>
          <li>
            No rush fees. Early turnaround available. (Typically 1-5 business
            days)
          </li>
          <li>
            Retainers at <strong>25 and 50 hours/month</strong>, with
            lower effective rates.
          </li>
          <li>Flexible usage: Concept, Design, Animation, Consulting.</li>
          <li>
            <strong>Client Portal Access:</strong> Central hub for requests, assets,
            and files.
          </li>
          <li>
            Up to <strong>10% of unused hours</strong> roll over to the next month,
            then expire.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Best for:</strong> Frequent presentation design needs.
          </li>
          <!-- <li>Excess hours billed at standard project basis rate.</li> -->
        </ul>
        <!-- <p class="engagement-card__note">
          <strong>Best for:</strong> Frequent presentation design needs.
        </p> -->
        <!-- <p class="engagement-card__note engagement-card__note--muted">
          Most retainer clients start with a <strong>3-month commitment</strong>
          so we can establish a rhythm and refine your preferences.
        </p> -->
        <p class="engagement-card__note engagement-card__note--muted">
          Limited availability · 3‑month minimum commitment · Custom retainers
          available on request
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
    <!-- <p class="engagement__footer-note">
      We’ll define detailed expectations for turnaround times, communication,
      and prioritization together during a short call.
    </p> -->
  </div>
</section>
